So before we start, some basic reminders / tips.
There's a bunch of stuff on Canvas, with links to a wiki and the how to play (top of the screen on desktop). Read that stuff once you get your role.
1) Do not discuss anything to do with this game outside of the game itself.
2) Some abilities are single use, some can be used every night. I would generally recommend using abilities that are multi-use every night. Single use stuff you should aim to pick your moment.

3) Scroll up to the top of the chat for each day, as the "morning report" will tell you who died, and if anything happened to you last night, plus give you reports for any abilities that you have used.

4) Day 1 is usually quite chill, as no one has done anything yet. We might get to see some information about the game, such as what roles are in, so the start of a plan could take place, but usually not. We can't lynch anyone on day 1.
Any other questions, now is a good time to ask.
also I've said it already a few times but...
5) Do NOT state who you are and start using meta to accuse people.
for example: "I'm Zahir, and I know that person is Mark because they spell like a dumb-dumb. I also know Mark wouldn't play this way, so we should lynch".
its too meta, and outside of the way to play the game.
This game has Werewolves, Bloodmoon Cult and Villagers. There are no other factions.
Wolfpack roles are taken from the following list: [Alphawolf, Bloodhound, Bloodletter, Bloodthirster, Direwolf, Shapeshifter, Werewolf]
Bloodmoon roles are taken from the following list: [BloodPriest, BloodSeer, CultAssassin, CultFollower, CultLeader]

The village roles are taken from the following list: [Adjudicator, Arcanist, Courtesan, Diseased, DrunkHarlot, DrunkSeer, DrunkStalker, Elder, Gravedigger, Harlot, Huntsman, IlluminatiLeader, Inquisitor, Insomniac, MapleWolf, MasonLeader, MasonSergeant, Messiah, Militia, Reviver,Seer, Sleepwalker, Stalker, StrongMan, Villager, Zealot]
There are no items or auras in this game.
Roles are not revealed on death.
Each role in the list can be picked multiple times, so there may be duplicates of some roles, and 0 of others.

Please remember, All discussion related to the game must happen here. You may not discuss anything to do with the game outside of the game, including to other players not in this specific game, or to other players in your team (if evil).

Single-use night actions can not be undone once activated in the game interface, so be sure you want to use it before pressing the button. You can change the target, but you can not go back to not using it.

You can not use out-of-game information in game, such as "I know PlayerX is Mark but I know Mark was watching a movie at the time they spoke today, so it couldn't possibly be them" this is considered meta.

If you have any questions about roles/the website/etc, believe there has been a bug, or are unsure of something, feel free to reach out to Dataforce#4726 on Discord or shane@werewolv.es and I'll reply as quick as I can. (I am UK Based but tend to keep US waking hours, so may not respond immediately.)
